Sarkozy, Merkel Spoke by Phone Today on Euro Area, Elysee Says

-- B y   H e l e n e   F o u q u e t
-- 
2011-10-22T14:06:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/sarkozy-merkel-spoke-by-phone-today-on-euro-area-elysee-says.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy  and
German  Chancellor Angela Merkel  spoke by phone today to discuss
the euro crisis, according to a spokesman for Sarkozy. They are
scheduled to meet European leaders tonight in Brussels, then at
a summit tomorrow and at an Oct. 26 summit intended to complete
a plan to address the debt contagion.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helene Fouquet in Paris at 
 hfouquet1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Hertling at 
 jhertling@bloomberg.net  